node.text:
Can you imagine being an environment such that when you walk down the street, everybody that sees you feels at home?

…You and I are environments for each other… we’re the soil in which the flowers around us grow.

- Ram Dass
@kheilawarheart @enfingaby The goddess of spring by Disney :)))
What's the name of this animation?
@noahinboston Have a look at the Ram Dass Here & Now podcast - Ep. 271 - Intuitive Rightness :)
I love love love this.  Does anybody have a link to the lecture or talk or interview that this is from?

@dariadreamz that's what I do too 🤍 and it doesn't matter how many tools and courses we master, it's this essence what truly impacts others, which we already have, so you are probably already doing this with all the people around you... 🙏🏻
@bri_t_ney really appreciate all the kind words and encouragement from everyone 🫶🏼🫶🏼

@anapaula.gz yes exactly. Sense of safety is paramount to process how we really feel, instead of normally rationalizing ourselves away from what we find uncomfortable in the body, collective and present moment 🙏🏼
This is how I’d want to approach my clients as a future therapist 🙏🏼💜
How beautiful 💕 this brought so much peace and softness and intentions to move with flowers around me….
💜💜💜 This is the Aura I achieve to shine as a professional and average being, a source of pure trustworthy light and love.
I wanted to be grown up in this goddess when I was a kid
